import React from 'react';
import { Redirect, Route } from 'react-router-dom';
import {
  IonIcon,
  IonLabel,
  IonPage,
  IonRouterOutlet,
  IonTabBar,
  IonTabButton,
  IonTabs,
  IonToolbar
} from '@ionic/react';
import { ellipse, square, triangle } from 'ionicons/icons';
import Tab1 from '../components/Tab1';
import Tab2 from '../components/Tab2';
import Tab1Detail from '../components/Tab1Detail';
import Tab3 from '../components/Tab3';
import TopNav from '../components/TopNav';
// import Tab1Detail from './Tab1Detail';


const ProgrammeTalksTab: React.FC = () => (
        <IonTabs>
            <IonRouterOutlet>
                <Route path="/u/openHouseMain/programmeTalksTab" component={Tab1} exact={true} />
                <Route path="/u/openHouseMain/programmeTalksTab/tab1-detail" component={Tab1Detail} exact={true} />
                <Route path="/u/openHouseMain/programmeTalksTab/tab2" component={Tab2} exact={true} />
                <Route path="/u/openHouseMain/programmeTalksTab/tab3" component={Tab3} exact={true} />
                <Route path="/" render={() => <Redirect to="/u/openHouseMain/programmeTalksTab" />} exact={true} />
            </IonRouterOutlet>

            <ion-tab tab="tab-three">
                <ion-header>
                    <ion-toolbar>
                    <ion-title>Tab Three</ion-title>
                    </ion-toolbar>

                    <ion-tab-bar>
                    <ion-tab-button tab="star-tab">
                        <ion-icon name="star"></ion-icon>
                    </ion-tab-button>

                    <ion-tab-button tab="globe-tab">
                        <ion-icon name="globe"></ion-icon>
                    </ion-tab-button>

                    <ion-tab-button tab="facebook-tab">
                        <ion-icon name="logo-facebook"></ion-icon>
                    </ion-tab-button>
                    </ion-tab-bar>

                </ion-header>

                <ion-content padding>
                    Tab Three
                </ion-content>

                </ion-tab>

            
            {/* <IonTabBar slot="bottom">
                <IonTabButton tab="tab1" href="/u/openHouseMain/programmeTalksTab">
                    <IonIcon icon={triangle} />
                    <IonLabel>Tab 1</IonLabel>
                </IonTabButton>
                <IonTabButton tab="tab2" href="/u/openHouseMain/programmeTalksTab/tab2">
                    <IonIcon icon={ellipse} />
                    <IonLabel>Tab 2</IonLabel>
                </IonTabButton>
                <IonTabButton tab="tab3" href="/u/openHouseMain/programmeTalksTab/tab3">
                    <IonIcon icon={square} />
                    <IonLabel>Tab 3</IonLabel>
                </IonTabButton>
            </IonTabBar> */}
        </IonTabs>
);

export default ProgrammeTalksTab;
